text: Bezirk Neusiedl am See (; ) is a district of the state of Burgenland in Austria. ==Municipalities== Towns (Städte) are indicated in boldface; market towns (Marktgemeinden) in italics; suburbs, hamlets and other subdivisions of a municipality are indicated in small characters.
